= El entierro

The coffin is closed, on instructions no one will put in writing. He was picked up on a Tuesday; he was delivered to his mother twelve days later with the paperwork calling it a road accident, and the family was advised, gently, by men with credentials, that a small funeral would be best for everyone.

The cemetery workers know the genre and dig quickly. The question is only how many stand at the grave, and how loudly the Internationale may be hummed.

- @multitud: Turn out everyone. Some things are answered with numbers.
- @intimo: The family, a flag folded small, and the list. The list above all: name, date, place. The Party keeps the list.

@multitud
